long.ar:
Goalkeeper Challenge is a browser football game made for you. We have 10 different levels of increasing difficulty at our disposal. Start the game to test your reflexes, and defend as many shots as possible. Everything is in your hands! 

To swipe Install this extension to play Goalkeeper Challenge game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact with us support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
